{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014EkeyWCoqMppJdfyxyReG6","type":"tool_result","content":"5. If clean: merges to main, cleans up the worktree, deletes the branch.\n6. If unresolvable: reports failure.\n\n**On the host via worktree:** Merges need direct access to the real git repo. A git\nworktree is created for the merge, then removed after completion. Lighter weight\nthan spinning up a container.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_019ypLfX9L3BfCTvo4W2Nw4T","session_id":"86005800-dc4f-4a50-b6ae-f82ea613cda8","uuid":"8dd841d4-78dd-4c27-b690-e0806eebacff"}
