{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014jkmeaAboC4KXsSBxKH8kP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nImplemented host workflow script execution from the main branch worktree. Changes:\n\n**`internal/host/executor.go`:**\n- Added `MainDir` field to `Executor` — the main worktree directory from which scripts execute\n- Added `scriptDir()` helper that returns `MainDir` if set, falling back to `ProjectDir`\n- Changed `executeScript` to use `scriptDir()` as `cmd.Dir` instead of `ProjectDir` directly\n- `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR` env var still points to `ProjectDir` (the actual worktree), so scripts can still access worktree-specific files\n- Added `MainWorktreeDir()` function that uses `git worktree list --porcelain` to find the main (non-linked) worktree path, falling back to `projectDir` if not a git repo\n\n**`internal/host/runner.go`:**\n- `RunWithID` now calls `MainWorktreeDir(projectDir)` and passes the result as `MainDir` to the `Executor`\n\n**`internal/host/executor_test.go`** — 6 new tests:\n- `TestExecutor_ScriptStep_UsesMainDir` — scripts resolve from MainDir\n- `TestExecutor_ScriptStep_MainDirOverridesProjectDir` — MainDir's script wins over ProjectDir's\n- `TestExecutor_ScriptStep_FallsBackToProjectDir` — empty MainDir falls back to ProjectDir\n- `TestExecutor_ScriptStep_ProjectDirEnvVar` — `CLOCHE_PROJECT_DIR` always points to ProjectDir\n- `TestMainWorktreeDir_NonGitDir` — non-git directory falls back\n- `TestMainWorktreeDir_WithWorktree` — real git worktree resolves to main worktree\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":287,"cache_read_input_tokens":53689,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":287},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86005800-dc4f-4a50-b6ae-f